articles.author: Hanna Ziady, Anna Cooban
articles.title: Europe finally agrees to cap gas prices - CNN
articles.description: Europe has agreed to a cap on natural gas prices, following months of debate over whether the measure will protect European households and businesses from extreme price spikes as temperatures plummet.
